snippet.title: New version – [Dreams of Gemina] - Honkai Impact 3rd
snippet.description:
The stage is set for the new S-rank battlesuit [Molotov Cherry] of Rozaliya and A-rank battlesuit [Blueberry Blitz] of Liliya, the star twins from Siberia!

The long lost ruins have emerged again. Summoned warriors, your journey starts here! [Honkai Kingdoms] is coming, and so is war!

Subscribe our YouTube and turn on notification for latest video : http://bit.ly/HonkaiImpact3rdYTB
